|     |
|     |--folder_01
|     |     |
|     |     |--file_01.v
|     |
|     |--folder_02
|
|--ex_02.pl
|
|--readme

2/ Requirement:

+ Delete all files in "folder_02"

+ Open file "ex_02.pl" by "VI" and compose a short script so as to copy "file_01" to "folder_02" and 
   + Change name to "file_02"
   + Replace "PARAMETER_WIDTH" input argument --> it may be 3 or 4 or any number

+ Guide: Use code : $PARAMETER_INPUT  = $ARGV[0]; # Variable "PARAMETER_INPUT" will receive input arguement

3/ How to run

   /usr/bin/perl ex_02.pl 10

4/ Expected result 

|--01_ex02
|     |
|     |--folder_01
|     |     |
|     |     |--file_01.v
|     |
|     |--folder_02
|           |
|           |--file_02.v  // In this file, the string "PARAMETER_WIDTH" is replaced by input argument --> In this example: 10
|     
|--ex_02.pl
|
|--readme
